title: Oops! Ranbir Kapoor and Katrina Kaif's 'Jagga Jagoos' has been delayed again! This time the reason is...
text:
Ranbir Kapoor and Katrina Kaif 
There has been talk that Ranbir Kapoor and Katrina Kaif's 'Jagga Jasoos' will be unable to hit screens on April 7 as planned.
Buzz is director Anurag Basu is yet to decide how and where the 29 songs of his musical will be placed. Four years in the making, 'Jagga Jasoos', which will mark RK's first production, is proving to be an endless wait for viewers.
